Changing the location back to sol b? No.  I don't think losing sleep is the best way to have fun (VI should really get slapped around by the law for exploiting an addiction and causing health problems).  Maybe make RF triggered and higher level, or make some of the other encounters for the cleric epic a little tougher.<br>
<br>
BTW, there may be items that are better than the epic in terms of stats, but what makes the Cleric Epic so handy is speedy CR time.  So here are your choices:<br>
<br>
1 - Stop arguing, go with how it is now and try and get an epic.<br>
2 - Come up with a plan (and actually ignore those who aren't in the majority), and get your epic.<br>
3 - Try things beyond an online petition and change things, then acquire your epic when things are changed.<br>
4 - Never get your epic and aim for something higher (In which case, actually learn a few tactics and get your hands on some MR2's and MGB's to make up for the effect)<br>
5 - Argue about it some more, getting no where, and making competition for your epic tougher because people start to hate you based on your views and won't think twice about KSing.<br>
<br>
~Molt<br>
